Agenda

Agenda

Afternoon (1:30PM)

  • Identification of key areas in which existing systems are unable to interoperate
  • Discussion of which key areas can be profitably addressed by this working group, and a rough prioritization of the areas
  • Solicitation of volunteers for coordinating work on improving interoperability in key areas
  • Development of criteria for evaluating the success of key area work groups
  • Establishing timelines for action
